    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I am writing to draw your attention to the issue of my laptop charger not working. I made a purchase of a new laptop on the 25 of December at your store in lotus road, attached is a copy of the receipt for your reference. However, the charging cable stopped working after two days of use, and ever since I am unable to use my laptop.",
        "This has indeed created a lot of trouble at my workplace, I was unable to attend a few meetings and finish my work on time. Moreover, I work from home and my laptop is very much crucial for my job, thus I require an immediate solution for this problem.",
        "Therefore, I urge you to deliver a new charger at your earliest to the same address which was provided at the time of purchase. Please consider this matter to be urgent thereby I expect your prompt action on this.",
        "Hoping to hear from you soon.",
        "Your\u2019s faithfully,",
        "Jack Fernando"
